name: WindSoundsforSleep
0:
”Alexa open wind sounds”
”Alexa ask wind sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: wind sounds
des: Woosh! Let the gusty sounds of wind lull you to sleep! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Wind Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
